channel.title: Rsps help for vps - please help! :(
channel.description:
Hey i need help running the Run.bat file on my CentOS vps, I dont know the command and ive been trying for hours! I would really appreciate if anyone could help me with this, here's the run.bat code.
[code]@echo off title PerishedPK "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_25\bin\java.exe" -cp bin;deps/poi.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar;deps/jython.jar;log4j-1.2.15.jar;-server -XX:+AggressiveHeap -XX:MaxHeapFreeRatio=90 -XX:MinHeapFreeRatio=90 -XX:+DisableExplicitGC -XX:+RelaxAccessControlCheck -XX:+UseParallelGC -XX:CompileThreshold=1 -XX:ThreadStackSize=128 server.Server pause[/code]
